title: AT&T scoops up Kyocera Hydro Air for GoPhone plans
text:
AT&T scoops up Kyocera Hydro Air for GoPhone plans 
Published By: AndroidGuys.com - Today 
AT&T is now selling the waterproof Kyocera Hydro Air as part of its GoPhone prepaid service. Priced $99, the phone runs Android 5.1 Lollipo...
